*Glupošću* je njegov život bio obilježen. (His life was marked by foolishness.)

*Glupom* se ponašanju nikad nije mogao oduprijeti. (He could never resist to foolish behavior.)

Nije znao da će se njegova *glupost* toliko osvetiti. (He didn't know that his foolishness will revenge so much.)

Razgovor je postao još neugodniji kada je izgovorio nešto *glupo*. (The conversation became even more unpleasant when he said something foolish.)

*Glupim* postupcima je sve više izazivao ljutnju. (He was increasingly provoking anger with foolish actions.)